1. *Ruka* mu se tresla kad je govorio o njoj. (His hand was shaking when he was talking about her.)
2. *Ruku* mu je pružila kako bi se zagrlili. (She stretched out her hand to hug him.)
3. Ona je podigla *ruke* u zrak. (She raised her hands in the air.)
4. Rekao je da će dati svoju *ruku* da se stvari promene. (He said he would lend a hand to change things.)
5. On je odlučio da drži *ruku* svojoj mami dok ona umire. (He decided to hold his mother's hand while she died.)